</ul>
</li>
<li><p><a class="reference internal" href="#using-role-dependencies" id="id14">Using role dependencies</a></p>
<ul>
<li><p><a class="reference internal" href="#running-role-dependencies-multiple-times-in-one-play" id="id15">Running role dependencies multiple times in one play</a></p></li>
